# hacker hive

## what?

housing cooperatives (like [BSC](http://bsc.coop)) modeled after [hackerspaces](http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/List_of_Hacker_Spaces)

## who?

hackers of Berkeley (see [Hack@Berkeley](http://hackersatberkeley.com/), CSUA, OCF, IEEE, and probably you)

## where?

[northside of UC Berkeley](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northside,_Berkeley,_California)

